data.description: Price Improvement! Assumable 3.875% Mortgage!  $3,000 seller credit when using preferred lender!  This is the one, a beautiful 5 bedroom 4 full bathroom 3,210 sqft. 2-story home is located in the stately neighborhood, "The Georgian" a golf cart community and home of the prestigious 18-hole Championship golf course "The Frog" designed by the legendary designer, and architect Tom Fazio. The Georgian truly offers a remarkable array of facilities including an amazing clubhouse, pro-shop, and restaurant as well as resort-style pools and water park, playgrounds, tennis courts, volleyball courts, and soccer fields. There are scenic parks and picturesque lush green spaces to connect with neighbors and friends. This can't miss home is also conveniently located in close proximity to schools, restaurants, grocery, and retail centers.   Upon entering the home's foyer, you'll find the coffered ceiling of the formal dining room across from French doors that open to the home office perfect for work-from-home needs. The large family room with fireplace opens to the breakfast area and the chef's kitchen which features stainless steel appliances, walk-in pantry, granite countertops, 42" cabinets, and large island perfect for entertaining. Downstairs also features a guest bedroom and full bathroom. Upstairs you'll find 2 more secondary bedrooms with a shared full bathroom, a secondary suite with private bathroom and a massive bonus room that's perfect for a home gym, office space, pajama lounge, or entertainment/gaming center. Also upstairs is the oversized primary suite which features a tray-ceiling and two large walk-in closets off the ensuite with tile shower, and large soaking tub.   The wonderful backyard offers a COVERED BACK PORCH and full privacy fence.    Don’t miss out on this opportunity to get all of this with an assumable 3.875% mortgage when using M&T Bank.    $3,000 seller credit when using Michael Anthony with Mutual of Omaha
